OL,3,CNetwork Rail warned monitoring
OL,4,Cequipment may not detect future
OL,5,Clandslips
OL,7,FAn investigation into the Shap train
OL,8,Fderailment has revealed that rail
OL,9,Fmonitoring equipment may not be able
OL,10,Fto adequately detect landslips.
OL,12,FThe Rail Accident Investigation Branch
OL,13,F(RAIB) has issued urgent safety
OL,14,Fadvice, saying that lineside
OL,15,Fmonitoring kit "may not be able to
OL,16,Fdetect the failure of slopes in some
OL,17,Fcircumstances," and that this issue
OL,18,Fwould be most likely in "severe
OL,19,Fweather conditions".
