OL,3,CNetwork Rail warned monitoring
OL,4,Cequipment may not detect future
OL,5,Clandslips
OL,7,FThis warning comes a day after a minor
OL,8,Flandslip disrupted services between
OL,9,FMillom and Corkickle on Thursday
OL,10,FDecember 18.
OL,12,FThe RAIB has instructed Network Rail
OL,13,Fand relevant infrastructure managers
OL,14,Fto "take urgent steps to consider and,
OL,15,Fif necessary, mitigate this risk".
