OL,3,CNetwork Rail warned monitoring
OL,4,Cequipment may not detect future
OL,5,Clandslips
OL,7,FIn addition, the RAIB also found that
OL,8,Fthe sensors' wireless signal was
OL,9,Funable to pass through the layer of
OL,10,Fdebris which had covered them in the
OL,11,Flandslip.
OL,13,FNetwork Rail has been approached for
OL,14,Fcomment.
